code: @Override public E next(E target) throws IOException {     E targetStaging = this.currentSource.next(target).     if (targetStaging != null) {         return targetStaging.     } else {         if (this.nextSources.size() > 0) {             this.currentSource = this.nextSources.remove(0).             return next(target).         } else {             return null.         }     } }

@Override public E next() throws IOException {     E targetStaging = this.currentSource.next().     if (targetStaging != null) {         return targetStaging.     } else {         if (this.nextSources.size() > 0) {             this.currentSource = this.nextSources.remove(0).             return next().         } else {             return null.         }     } }
